## Import



Using `pulumi import`, import `aws_neptune_cluster_snapshot` using the cluster snapshot identifier. For example:

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:neptune/clusterSnapshot:ClusterSnapshot example my-cluster-snapshot
```
